# Optional: override the default password (123456) for local development.
# If not set, the project uses a built-in default password.
#
# To set a custom password:
# 1. Run: node scripts/hash-password.mjs YOUR_PASSWORD
# 2. Copy the output hash below
# ACCESS_PASSWORD_HASH=sha256:YOUR_HASH_HERE
#
# SESSION_SECRET is optional for local dev (a default is used).
# In production, set this to a random 32+ character string.
# SESSION_SECRET=your-random-secret-key